<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 id="faq-heading">FAQ</h2>

        <div class="faq">
            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>What areas does Call Dan service?</summary>
                <p>
                    Call Dan provides handyman services throughout South West
                    Sydney, including Penrith, St Marys, Mount Druitt,
                    Parramatta, Merrylands, Fairfield, Cabramatta, Liverpool,
                    Prestons, Ingleburn, Minto, Leumeah, Campbelltown, Mount
                    Annan, Leppington, Austral, Keeps Creek, and Glenmore Park.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary
                    >How much does Call Dan charge for handyman services?</summary
                >
                <p>
                    We provide affordable and transparent pricing with no hidden
                    costs. Contact us today for a free, no obligation quote
                    tailored to your specific handyman needs.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>Do you offer emergency handyman services?</summary>
                <p>
                    Yes. Call Dan offers prompt and reliable emergency handyman
                    services for urgent repairs and maintenance tasks around
                    your home or business.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary
                    >Can Call Dan handle multiple handyman tasks at once?</summary
                >
                <p>
                    Absolutely. Call Dan specialises in tackling multiple
                    handyman jobs in one convenient visit, saving you time and
                    money.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>How quickly can Call Dan attend to my job?</summary>
                <p>
                    We pride ourselves on fast response times and often provide
                    same day handyman services. Contact us now to arrange your
                    service quickly.
                </p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section#faq {
        background-color: #000; /* Black background */
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
        color: #fff; /* Default text color */
    }

    section#faq .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    #faq-heading {
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #ffd600; /* Yellow accent for heading */
    }

    /* FAQ items grid */
    .faq {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    /* Each accordion panel */
    .faq-item {
        border: 1px solid #444; /* Dark grey border */
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-color: transparent;
    }

    /* Summary (the question) */
    .faq-item summary {
        list-style: none; /* remove default marker */
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #fff;
        user-select: none;
    }

    /* Hide the browser’s default marker */
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
    }

    /* Custom arrow icon */
    .faq-item summary::after {
        content: "▾"; /* down-caret */
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #ffd600;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    /* Rotate arrow when open */
    .faq-item[open] summary::after {
        transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    /* The answer text */
    .faq-item p {
        padding: 0 1.25rem 1rem;
        color: #ddd;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    summary {
        line-height: 165%;
    }
</style>
